                 = XQJL0331-O-ONCP-BSAMT / 1000000
      *@자기자본기준년월
           MOVE XQJL0331-O-BASE-YM
             TO XDJL4033-O-ONCP-BASE-YM
           .
       S3300-QJL0331-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
