             TO XQJL0332-I-PYY-END(1:4)
           MOVE CO-CHA-12
             TO XQJL0332-I-PYY-END(5:2)
      *@   전월
           MOVE XCJIDT17-O-BF-YMD(1:6)
             TO XQJL0332-I-LSMN-END

      *@3.3 프로그램　호출
           #DYSQLA QJL0332 XQJL0332-CA

      *@3.4 호출결과　확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
      *@원장조회에러인경우
      *@에러메세지 : 테이블 SELECT 오류입니다．
      *@조치메세지 : 전산업무담당자에게　문의바랍니다
                    #ERROR CO-B4200223 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
           END-EVALUATE

      *@3.5 출력변수 MOVE

      *@   출력건수
           MOVE DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
             TO XDJL4033-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *@   OUTPUT LOOP
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1
             UNTIL WK-I > XDJL4033-O-OUTPT-LINE-CNT1

      *@           계열코드                                           03550002
                   MOVE XQJL0332-O-AFFLT-CORP-GROUP-CD(WK-I)            03560002
                     TO XDJL4033-O-AFFLT-CORP-GROUP-CD(WK-I)            03570002
      *@           계열명                                             03580002
                   MOVE XQJL0332-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME(WK-I)             03590002
                     TO XDJL4033-O-AFFLT-C-GROUP-NAME(WK-I)             03600002
      *@           전년말잔액(은행기준)                             03610002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-PYY-END-GRCR(WK-I)
                         = XQJL0332-O-PYY-END-AMT (WK-I) / 1000000
      *@           전월잔액(은행기준)                               03640002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-LSMN-END-GRCR(WK-I)
                         = XQJL0332-O-LSMN-AMT(WK-I) / 1000000
      *@           당월잔액（은행기준）                               03670002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-TTMM-END-GRCR(WK-I)
                         = XQJL0332-O-TTMN-AMT(WK-I) / 1000000
      *@           전월말대비증감                                     03670002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-LSMN-E-CNTST-INCRDC(WK-I)
                         = XDJL4033-O-TTMM-END-GRCR(WK-I) -
                           XDJL4033-O-LSMN-END-GRCR(WK-I)
      *@           전년말대비증감                                     03670002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-PYY-E-CNTST-INCRDC(WK-I)
                         = XDJL4033-O-TTMM-END-GRCR(WK-I) -
                           XDJL4033-O-PYY-END-GRCR(WK-I)
      *@           자기자본대비신용공여율                             03670002
                   IF XDJL4033-O-ONCP-BSAMT > 0
                   COMPUTE WK-EXHS-RT
                         = XDJL4033-O-TTMM-END-GRCR(WK-I) /
                           XDJL4033-O-ONCP-BSAMT
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-ONCP-CNTST-GRCR-RT(WK-I)
                         = WK-EXHS-RT * 100
                   ELSE
                   MOVE ZERO
                     TO XDJL4033-O-ONCP-CNTST-GRCR-RT(WK-I)
                   END-IF

      *@           신용공여규모순위                                   03670002
                   MOVE WK-I
                     TO XDJL4033-O-GRCR-SCAL-RANKG(WK-I)
                                                                        03700002
           END-PERFORM
           .
       S3400-QJL0332-CALL-EXT.
           EXIT.
