      *@           전월잔액(금감원기준)                             03640002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-LSMN-END-GRCR(WK-I)
                         = XQJL0333-O-LSMN-AMT(WK-I) / 1000000
      *@           당월잔액（금감원기준）                             03670002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-TTMM-END-GRCR(WK-I)
                         = XQJL0333-O-TTMN-AMT(WK-I) / 1000000
      *@           전월말대비증감                                     03670002
                   COMPUTE XDJL4033-O-LSMN-E-CNTST-INCRDC(WK-I)
